 |title=Protests As Anger Over Bahrain F1 Race Grows |url=http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16212342 |work=[[Sky_News|Sky News Online]] |publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]] |date=2012-04-20 |accessdate=2012-04-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423030803/http://news.sky.com/home/world-news/article/16212342 |archivedate=2012-04-23 }}</ref>形容為「頗具爭議性」。《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》更稱這場賽事是「體育歷史上最具爭議的比賽之一」。<ref>{{cite news|title=Rage against the Formula One machine|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/rage-against-the-formula-one-machine-7665991.html|first1=Jerome|last1=Taylor|first2=David|last2=Tremayne|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|publisher=Independent Print Limited|date=2012-04-21|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712223934/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/rage-against-the-formula-one-machine-7665991.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==影響這場比賽的事件==

===2011年的取消及2012年的恢復===
[[2011年巴林大獎賽|2011年巴林大獎賽]]由於2011年2月21日的民間動亂，<ref>{{cite news |title=Bahrain Grand Prix off after anti-government protest |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9402871.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2012-04-02 |date=2011-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110224052658/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9402871.stm |archivedate=2011-02-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>在王儲[[薩勒曼·本·哈邁德·本·伊薩·阿勒哈利法|薩勒曼·本·哈邁德·本·伊薩·阿勒哈利法]]和巴林汽車聯盟的要求下被取消。<ref>{{cite news |title=Bahrain Grand Prix off after anti-government protest |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9402871.stm |work=BBC Sport |accessdate=2012-04-21 |date=2011-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110224052658/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/formula_one/9402871.stm |archivedate=2011-02-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>在[[國際汽聯世界汽車運動理事會|國際汽聯世界汽車運動理事會]]試圖於十月恢復比賽未成的一個月後，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/91492|title=F1 ponders Dec 4 slot for Indian GP|first1=Jonathan|last1=Noble|first2=Dieter|last2=Rencken|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2011-05-19|accessdate=2012-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231946/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/91492|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/92109|title=Bahrain gives up on 2011 race|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2011-06-09|accessdate=2012-03-25|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|archive-date=2017-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812211423/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/92109|dead-url=no}}</ref>國際汽聯發布一份暫定的2012年賽曆，再度安排了巴林大獎賽。賽事最初定在11月舉行，以便等到安定後再重返該國。<ref name="FIA reveals 21-race calendar for 2012">{{cite news |url=http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/261352/fia-reveals-21-race-calendar-for-2012/ |title=FIA reveals 21-race calendar for 2012 |work=gpupdate.net |publisher=GPUpdate |date=2011-06-03 |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iqi0LBj?url=http://www.gpupdate.net/en/f1-news/261352/fia-reveals-21-race-calendar-for-2012/ |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>第二份暫定賽曆於7月發布，其中巴林大獎賽被提前到了4月22日。<ref>{{cite news|title=2012 Formula 1 season opener keeps March 18 slot despite overhaul|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/93453|first=Pablo|last=Elizalde|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2011-07-29|accessdate=2012-03-25|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022005444/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/93453|dead-url=no}}</ref>接著，在2011年12月最終賽程表公布後正式敲定。<ref name="7Dec calendar">{{cite news |url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2011/12/07/united-states-grand-prix-remains-unchanged-2012-f1-calendar/ |title=United States Grand Prix remains on unchanged 2012 F1 calendar |first=Keith |last=Collantine |work=F1 Fanatic |publisher=Keith Collantine |date=2011-12-07 |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iqkH8np?url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2011/12/07/united-states-grand-prix-remains-unchanged-2012-f1-calendar/ |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

隨著2012年賽季的季前測試於2012年2月展開，巴林大獎賽的未來再度成為了媒體炒作的議題。許多車隊早在[[2011年日本大獎賽|2011年日本大獎賽]]時便對該國的情勢表示關切，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/95191|title=Teams express concern over ongoing political situation in Bahrain|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2011-10-09|accessdate=2012-03-25|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223758/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/95191|dead-url=no}}</ref>而{{le|巴林人權中心|Bahrain Centre for Human Rights}}也力勸各隊在該國再度發生的政治動亂中，聯合抵制這場比賽，<ref>{{cite news |title=F1 teams urged to boycott Bahrain Grand Prix |url=http://www.arabianbusiness.com/f1-teams-urged-boycott-bahrain-grand-prix-438970.html |first=Claire |last=Ferris-lay |work=Arabian Business |publisher=ITP Publishing Group |date=2012-01-08 |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iqlhUkF?url=http://www.arabianbusiness.com/f1-teams-urged-boycott-bahrain-grand-prix-438970.html |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>並聲稱巴林政府試圖利用這場比賽來展現出該國當前情勢仍處穩定。[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]則堅持他繼續舉辦這場比賽的立場，而{{le|1996年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1996 Formula One season|1996年}}[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|世界冠軍]][[戴蒙·希爾|戴蒙·希爾]]也表示，他相信在造訪過該國之後，一級方程式賽車可以「心安理得」的重返巴林。<ref name="Damon">{{cite news |title=Bernie Ecclestone unchanged on Bahrain stance |url=http://www.thenational.ae/sport/formula-one/bernie-ecclestone-unchanged-on-bahrain-stance#full |first=Gary |last=Meenaghan |work=The National |publisher=Mubadala Development Company |date=2012-02-19 |accessdate=2012-03-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/65iqisbh5?url=http://www.thenational.ae/sport/formula-one/bernie-ecclestone-unchanged-on-bahrain-stance#full |archivedate=2012-02-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>然而，希爾在兩週後改變了他的立場，指出這場比賽「產生出的問題可能比已經解決的來得多」。<ref name="Hill opposed">{{cite news|title=Damon Hill voices fresh concern over staging Bahrain Grand Prix|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2012/apr/04/f1-bahrain-grand-prix|first=Paul|last=Weaver|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian News and Media|date=2012-04-04|accessdate=2012-04-05|archive-date=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112061123/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/2012/apr/04/f1-bahrain-grand-prix|dead-url=no}}</ref>他進一步闡述並告誡切勿對此「漠不關心」，也力勸這項運動不該有政治介入。<ref name="indifference">{{cite news|title=Damon Hill says Formula 1 cannot afford to be 'indifferent' about Bahrain situation|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98650|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-07|accessdate=2012-04-08|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022010618/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98650|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外，前世界冠軍[[傑奇·史都華|傑奇·史都華]]亦表示他支持舉辦這場比賽，並警告說相較於舉辦比賽，取消大獎賽可能會對這項運動造成更大的損失。<ref name="Jackie">{{cite news|title=Jackie Stewart in plea to save Bahrain Grand Prix|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/jackie-stewart-in-plea-to-save-bahrain-grand-prix.17276323|first=Marissa|last=Duffy|work=The Glasgow Herald|publisher=Newsquest|date=2012-04-11|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2012-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120413232712/http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/jackie-stewart-in-plea-to-save-bahrain-grand-prix.17276323|dead-url=no}}</ref>
