itle=Ed Miliband calls for cancellation of Bahrain Grand Prix|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/9216543/Ed-Miliband-calls-for-cancellation-of-Bahrain-Grand-Prix.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111190610/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/9216543/Ed-Miliband-calls-for-cancellation-of-Bahrain-Grand-Prix.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Yvette Cooper calls for Bahrain Grand Prix to be cancelled ahead of further violent protests|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/news/world/yvette-cooper-calls-for-bahrain-grand-prix-to-be-cancelled-ahead-of-further-violent-protests-7664488.html|work=London Evening Standard|publisher=ES London Limited|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2019-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911193113/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/world/yvette-cooper-calls-for-bahrain-grand-prix-to-be-cancelled-ahead-of-further-violent-protests-7664488.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在寫給[[紅牛公司|紅牛公司]]及[[新聞集團_(1979－2013年)|新聞集團]]-{zh-hans:首席执行官; zh-hant:執行長; zh-cn:首席执行官; zh-hk:行政總裁; zh-tw:執行長; zh-mo:行政總裁;}-[[迪特里希·馬特希茨|迪特里希·馬特希茨]]與[[魯柏·梅鐸|魯柏·梅鐸]]的信中，{{le|影子內閣外交大臣|Shadow Foreign Secretary}}[[道格拉斯·亞歷山大|道格拉斯·亞歷山大]]敦促各車隊、媒體和贊助商聯合抵制這場賽事。<ref name="MP-1"/>儘管沒有明確提到這場大獎賽，[[白宮|白宮]]仍舊譴責衝突雙方的暴力行為。<ref name="Yates"/>4月19日，包含[[殼牌公司|殼牌公司]]、[[沃達豐|沃達豐]]、[[瑞銀集團|瑞銀集團]]等的一些贊助商表示，將不會利用這場比賽來招待客戶和合作夥伴。<ref name="sponsors">{{cite news|title=Companies shun Bahrain Grand Prix hospitality|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/04/19/bahrain-grandprix-sponsors-idUKL6E8FJDXE20120419|first1=Tom|last1=Bergin|first2=Keith|last2=Weir|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|publisher=[[Thomson_Reuters|Thomson Reuters]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2014-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402014821/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2012/04/19/bahrain-grandprix-sponsors-idUKL6E8FJDXE20120419|dead-url=no}}</ref>企業招待會所也從這場比賽中撤出，其中有些更歷經了高達百分之八十的業績衰退。<ref name="sponsors"/>

國際汽聯主席[[尚·陶德|尚·陶德]]仍舊堅持著他認為該國安全無虞的立場，並提到「很顯然地，這場大獎賽可以照常舉辦。雖然一直有著關於這場比賽的爭議，但國際汽聯是一個體育組織。我們只關心體育，而非政治」。<ref name="MP-2"/>[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]更延續說這個國家很「寧靜祥和」，即便警方必須在比賽前幾天使用閃光彈來解散兩百餘位流氓的暴力集團，以及稱作「[[阿拉伯之春|憤怒日]]」的暴徒。<ref>{{cite news|title=Activists call for days of rage as F1 arrives in Bahrain|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/apr/18/f1-bernie-ecclestone-bahrain-peaceful|first=Paul|last=Weaver|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=2012-04-18|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2012-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814232634/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/apr/18/f1-bernie-ecclestone-bahrain-peaceful|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===車隊抵達巴林===
{{quote box|quote=「我相信國際汽聯，他們知道所有的資訊——我並不清楚，這僅是個人看法——所以我們必須信任他們的決定。我不認為他們會想把我們置於危險之中。就這條賽道、這些車輛等等來說，他們在車手身上做了許多安全措施，且這也是他們的首要之務。所以，我相信國際汽聯的決定。如果一切都很順利且沒有發生任何事，我甚至根本不用把這事放在心上。」|source={{F1|2009}}[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|世界冠軍]][[簡森·巴頓|簡森·巴頓]]，表示他相信國際汽聯照常舉辦這場比賽的決定。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain Grand Prix 2012: I trust in the FIA over decision to go ahead with Formula One race, says Jenson Button|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/9211516/Bahrain-Grand-Prix-2012-I-trust-in-the-FIA-over-decision-to-go-ahead-with-Formula-One-race-says-Jenson-Button.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002064355/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/9211516/Bahrain-Grand-Prix-2012-I-trust-in-the-FIA-over-decision-to-go-ahead-with-Formula-One-race-says-Jenson-Button.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>|width=35%|align=right}}
第一批車隊人員在4月17日抵達巴林，當日報導指出60位什葉派示威領袖已經在比賽前被捕。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain arrests protest leaders ahead of F1 amid torture|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/sportsNews/idAFJOE83H03K20120418|first=Andrew|last=Hammond|work=Reuters Africa|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2012-04-18|accessdate=2012-04-18|archive-date=2012-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424092552/http://af.reuters.com/article/sportsNews/idAFJOE83H03K20120418|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="xevi">{{cite news|title=@xevipujolar — 17 April|url=https://twitter.com/#!/xevipujolar/statuses/192195203128500225|first=Xevi|last=Pujolar|work=@xevipujolar|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-17|accessdate=2012-04-18|archive-date=2016-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103181657/https://twitter.com/notch/status/192755231275229185#!/xevipujolar/statuses/192195203128500225|dead-url=no}}</ref>車隊在為前往巴林作準備時，採取了額外的安全預防措施，包括僱用當地安全專家和策劃從首都[[麥納瑪|-{zh-hans:麦纳麦; zh-hant:麥納瑪;}-]]到賽道約{{convert|40|km|1}}的專家路程。<ref>{{cite news|title=@adamcooperf1 — 19 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperf1/status/192878106216906752|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=@adamcooperf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperf1/status/192878106216906752|dead-url=no}}</ref>通訊社[[法新社|法新社]]報導，他們的記者和攝影師被阻止進入巴林，而也有一些外國記者的簽證被延期，以防止他們進入該國。法新社更進一步報導，所有操作攝影機的人員被要求隨時攜帶高能見度的標誌，以便於清楚地辨認他們，並防止他們在賽道之外進行報導。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain denies visas to foreign journalists for F1|url=http://uk.news.yahoo.com/bahrain-denies-visas-foreign-journalists-f1-162721343.html|work=Yahoo! News|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]|agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419203810/http://uk.news.yahoo.com/bahrain-denies-visas-foreign-journalists-f1-162721343.html|archivedate=2012-04-19}}</ref>而那些經批准進入巴林的記者則轉向使用[[社會化媒體|社會化媒體]]網站，以規避新聞審查制度。<ref name="Cary Sauber">{{cite web|title=@tomcary_tel — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/tomcary_tel/status/193292073376555009|first=Tom|last=Cary|work=@tomcary_tel|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/tomcary_tel/status/193292073376555009|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Parkes Sauber">{{cite web|title=@ianparkesf1 — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/ianparkesf1/status/193298741032267776|first=Ian|last=Parkes|work=@ianparkesf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/ianparkesf1/status/193298741032267776|dead-url=no}}</ref>報導指出從-{zh-hans:麦纳麦; zh-hant:麥納瑪;}-到賽道沿路上有包含了[[裝甲|裝甲車輛]]和[[鎮暴警察|鎮暴警察]]的大量警力。<ref>{{cite web|title=@easonF1 — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/easonF1/status/193245741932744704|first=Kevin|last=Eason|work=@easonF1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/easonF1/status/193245741932744704|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯]]車手[[帕斯托·馬爾多納多|帕斯托·馬爾多納多]]的比賽工程師夏維·普喬拉（Xevi Pujolar）<ref>{{cite web|title=Xevi Pujolar – Race Engineer, Maldonado|url=http://www.williamsf1.com/team/profiles/xevi-pujolar-race-engineer-maldonado|work=[[Williams_F1|Williams F1]]|publisher=Williams Grand Prix Engineering|accessdate=2012-04-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120424050944/http://www.williamsf1.com/team/profiles/xevi-pujolar-race-engineer-maldonado|archivedate=2012-04-24}}</ref>將一張相片上傳至[[Twitter|Twitter]]，並記述「外頭一切安全」。<ref name="xevi"/>同時，[[HRT車隊|HRT]]車手及{{le|大獎賽車手協會|Grand Prix Drivers' Association}}主席[[佩德羅·德·拉·羅薩|佩德羅·德·拉·羅薩]]也談到他並不擔心這場賽事的安全。<ref>{{cite news|title=De la Rosa: No worries on driver safety in Bahrain|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98960|first=Edd|last=Straw|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304001030/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98960|dead-url=no}}</ref>衛冕世界冠軍[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]補充說，他覺得巴林不比[[巴西|巴西]]來得危險；<ref name="Barrichello">{{cite news|title=Rubens Barrichello hits out at those comparing Bahrain and Brazil safety|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98974|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223840/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98974|dead-url=no}}</ref>2009年世界冠軍簡森·巴頓在[[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]的[[2010年巴西大獎賽|2010年巴西大獎賽]]期間被捲入一起事件當中，在他離開賽道之後，一名武裝持槍者試圖劫持他的轎車。<ref>{{cite news|title=Jenson Button unhurt after armed men threaten him|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-11704802|work=BBC Sport|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2010-11-07|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114232925/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-11704802|dead-url=no}}</ref>維泰爾的言論引起了前車手[[魯本斯·巴里切羅|魯本斯·巴里切羅]]的批評，他表示巴西跟巴林根本無法相比。<ref name="Barrichello"/>包括了巴頓、[[麥可·舒馬克|麥可·舒馬克]]和[[羅曼·格羅斯讓|羅曼·格羅斯讓]]等一些車手拒絕再對巴林的政治局勢發表言論，並重申他們相信體育與當地政治應該有所區隔。<ref name="Barrichello"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Thursday's press conference – Bahrain|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98976|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303212926/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98976|dead-url=no}}</ref>在《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的一篇評論文章中，記者[[員羅柏·費斯克|員羅柏·費斯克]]嚴厲抨擊車手抱持他們的中立立場，稱賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾「無知」，並指責簡森·巴頓與路易斯·漢米爾頓持雙重標準，又得出結論認為21世紀的體育界人士再也無力疏遠道德價值觀。<ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Fisk: This is politics not sport. If drivers can't see that, they are the pits|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/fisk/robert-fisk-this-is-politics-not-sport-if-drivers-cant-see-that-they-are-the-pits-7665994.html|first=Robert|last=Fist=work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|publisher=Independent Print Limited|date=2012-04-21|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2012-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614204521/http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/commentators/fisk/robert-fisk-this-is-politics-not-sport-if-drivers-cant-see-that-they-are-the-pits-7665994.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在這場大獎賽的墊場賽——{{le|2012年保時捷超級盃賽季|2012 Porsche Supercup season}}開幕戰出戰的{{le|保時捷超級盃|Porsche Supercup}}車隊MRS車隊（MRS Racing）於4月18日退出比賽，理由是他們擔心該國的安全。<ref>{{cite news|title=Porsche Supercup squad MRS withdraws from Bahrain citing fears about safety|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98952|first=Sam|last=Tremayne|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-18|accessdate=2012-24-18|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221258/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98952|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===印度威力汽油炸彈事件===
{{quote box|quote=「我們是從能確保大家安康，及每個就位的人都能舒適的觀點來看待這件事。而這正是我們的首要目標。各位都知道，我們一直存在著問題，且我們必須確保組員在此環境下是舒適的，這也正是我們持續在做的事情。但是組員完全投入了排位賽和正賽的工作，且如果是這樣，為了達成這點將會限制或無法參加第二階段練習賽，所以我們必須做出抉擇。我們正在盡我們的所能來確保組員的安全。我們有把握達成，且我相信這不會有任何問題。而這裡將會有示威活動，我認為這是一起不幸的事件，但不幸的事件終究發生了。當它發生在你的車隊上，你必須以適當的方法來處理，這也是我們正在做的。|source=[[印度威力車隊|印度威力車隊]]代理主席{{le|鮑勃·弗利|Bob Fernley}}決定不參加週五的第二階段練習賽。<ref name="FIFP2"/><ref name="No FI"/>|width=35%|align=right}}
4月18日，前[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]]機械師、轉任記者的馬克·普里斯特利（Marc Priestley）在Twitter上報導，[[印度威力車隊|印度威力]]技工使用的出租汽車被捲入一起汽油爆炸事件，<ref>{{cite news|title=@f1elvis — 18 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/f1elvis/status/192701572298452993|first=Marc|last=Priestley|work=@f1elvis|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-18|accessdate=2012-04-18|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/f1elvis/status/192701572298452993|dead-url=no}}</ref>所幸沒有傷亡或財產損失。<ref>{{cite news|title=@f1elvis — 18 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/f1elvis/status/192725462814957568|first=Marc|last=Priestley|work=@f1elvis|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-18|accessdate=2012-04-18|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/f1elvis/status/192725462814957568|dead-url=no}}</ref>該隊一直使用著一輛沒有任何標誌的汽車往返兩地，<ref>{{cite news|title=@adamcooperf1 — 19 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperf1/status/192877576744730624|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=@adamcooperf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperf1/status/192877576744730624|dead-url=no}}</ref>且在附近發生汽油爆炸事件之前，他們被一個無法移除的臨時路障耽擱住。<ref>{{cite news|title=@adamcooperf1 — 19 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperF1/statuses/192876895044517888|first=Adam|last=Cooper|work=@adamcooperf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperF1/statuses/192876895044517888|dead-url=no}}</ref>這起事件的進一步報導指出，技工曾短暫接觸到安全部隊朝抗議者施放的[[催淚彈|催淚彈]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Force India car flees petrol bomb protest|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/17767985|first=Andrew|last=Benson|work=BBC Sport|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2015-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806163016/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/formula1/17767985|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中一位捲入風波的車隊成員在隔日便飛離該國。<ref>{{cite news|title=@easonF1 — 19 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperF1/statuses/192876895044517888|first=Kevin|last=Eason|work=@easonF1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/adamcooperF1/statuses/192876895044517888|dead-url=no}}</ref>這名未具名的技工在該國不再感到舒適，因此選擇離去。<ref>{{cite news|title=Force India member leaves Bahrain after incident|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98957|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2016-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161218152120/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98957|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二名技工也在幾個小時後離開。<ref>{{cite news|title=F1 mechanics flee Bahrain after petrol bomb attack during street protest|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/f1-mechanics-flee-bahrain-after-petrol-bomb-attack-during-street-protest-7661468.html|first1=David|last1=Tremayne|first2=Jerome|last2=Taylor|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|publisher=Independent Print Limited|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2016-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130170032/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/f1-mechanics-flee-bahrain-after-petrol-bomb-attack-during-street-protest-7661468.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>印度威力車手[[尼古拉斯·賀根堡|尼古拉斯·賀根堡]]對這一連串的事件感到不安，並且提到讓車隊成員擔心自身安全是「不對的」。<ref>{{cite news|title=Nico Hulkenberg says it's not right that F1 team members have to fear for their safety in Bahrain|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98963|first1=Jonathan|last1=Noble|first2=Pablo|last2=Elizalde|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2012-04-19|archive-date=2016-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161120075058/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98963|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在週五早上的第一階段自由練習賽結束不久後，媒體推測認為印度威力將不會參加當日晚些時候展開的第二階段自由練習賽，因為他們不放心在天黑後回到-{zh-hans:麦纳麦; zh-hant:麥納瑪;}-。<ref>{{cite web|title=@andrewbensonf1 — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/andrewbensonf1/status/193255647192678400|first=Andrew|last=Benson|work=@andrewbensonf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/andrewbensonf1/status/193255647192678400|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=@jamesallenonf1 — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/Jamesallenonf1/status/193260824784150530|first=James|last=Allen|work=@jamesallenonf1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/Jamesallenonf1/status/193260824784150530|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=@noblef1 — 20 April|url=http://twitter.com/#!/NobleF1/status/193260314492551168|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=@noblef1|publisher=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209172025/https://twitter.com/#!/NobleF1/status/193260314492551168|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然第二階段會在當地時間15時30分結束，但車隊還必須收拾維修站車庫，不可能在週五下午前離開賽道，勢必會遇上一些大型有組織的[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]示威遊行（抑或是「憤怒日」）。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Bahrain moves to foil anti-government rallies|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/bahrain-moves-to-foil-anti-government-rallies/2011/02/13/ABrXVXG_story.html|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|publisher=Katharine Weymouth; [[The_Washington_Post_Company|The Washington Post Company]]|date=2011-02-13|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109200531/http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/bahrain-moves-to-foil-anti-government-rallies/2011/02/13/ABrXVXG_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://arabnews.com/middleeast/article250370.ece |title=Yemenis