m/#!/NobleF1/status/193265282909868032|dead-url=no}}</ref>最終，車隊決定不參加第二階段練習賽。<ref name="No FI">{{cite news|title=Bahrain Grand Prix 2012: Force India to skip practice session over safety fears|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/9216112/Bahrain-Grand-Prix-2012-Force-India-to-skip-practice-session-over-safety-fears.html|first=Tom|last=Cary|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]]|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002073111/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/motorsport/formulaone/9216112/Bahrain-Grand-Prix-2012-Force-India-to-skip-practice-session-over-safety-fears.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過，該隊依舊維持他們贊同舉辦比賽的決定。<ref>{{cite news|title=Force India backs decision to go ahead with the Bahrain Grand Prix|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98985|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145803/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98985|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]對該隊決定退出第二階段練習賽的決定感到困惑，並指出沒有其他車隊表示擔憂他們的安全，且他也曾提議陪伴印度威力人員返回-{zh-hans:麦纳麦; zh-hant:麥納瑪;}-，不過卻遭到他們拒絕。<ref name="Bernie unmoved">{{cite news|title=Ecclestone unmoved by safety concerns in Bahrain as Force India pulls out of practice|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98991|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2012-04-20|accessdate=2012-04-20|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924145804/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/98991|dead-url=no}}</ref>

